{"tid":164680,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"［電腦白痴］電腦開唔到機","createTime":"2017-03-21T00:11:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T06:56:30.000Z","uid":32165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5f1735fc3b587c60465d687f5c7c654f04dbcc43","tid":164680,"uid":32165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T00:11:27.000Z","msg":"是咁的，想問一下各位巴打關於電腦開唔到機問題<br />\n部電腦尋晚按開機掣之後著一下燈run一下就停 之後不停重覆著一下 就停 又著一下<br />\n（好似噠車咁 不停自己噠 但開唔到車）<br />\n拆開左 desktop 機箱黎睇 CPU風扇郁一郁就停又郁<br />\n底板燈都著<br />\n我都對電腦認識極淺<br />\n盡可能將遇到既問題狀況講出來<br />\n<br />\n想問各位巴打有無試過以上情況<br />\n知唔知壞左啲咩<br />\n<br />\n謝謝各位解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723e9a2236d8274805ca6fef7908c5dcf4d540c4","tid":164680,"uid":4404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:32:38.000Z","msg":"雖然唔識 但見你咁慘就幫你推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0434f55b4b25b79c639e70c590eddcf7a563e99a","tid":164680,"uid":4404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:33:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bbd11b3e0d5b9e603ec18953f6bbed10f1ad510b","tid":164680,"uid":4404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:33:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07040c629d57cf65edae2eb8ce7a498135d9ff31","tid":164680,"uid":69416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:34:39.000Z","msg":"線鬆左 拆開機箱插番實D線<br />\n利申9up"},{"pid":"d8074dde8ce6992c86024b8bae223071c6168e25","tid":164680,"uid":10359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:35:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91bce50b0a6dc48d99f94f6dd8d954a2d4dd0efb","tid":164680,"uid":92074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:04:03.000Z","msg":"火牛問題<br />\n利申9up"},{"pid":"91d64a25ff8d5dd7440b06274da133136790e93b","tid":164680,"uid":81703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20